Lasko-Harwill and R. Stava，1994，“Virtual
realityand surgery，”to
appear in Computer Interated Surgery，Taylor，Lavallee，Burdea
and Moesges（editors），MIT
press.
4. S. Pieper，S.
Delp，J.
